  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','property_tour','Keeley Palm Jumeirah Villa Reel','Walking you through one of Palm Jumeirah''s most exclusive villas. Where design, detail, and lifestyle come together effortlessly. #PalmJumeirah #DubaiLuxury #LuxuryRealEstate #VillaTour #EREHomes','2026-04-01','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','behind_scenes','Agents Meeting about Contract','Building experts, not just agents. Learning the contract process because one deal smarter at a time. #EREHomes #Dubairealestate #learning #smart #realestate','2026-04-02','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','market_update','Keeley and Edna — Planning To Buy Property in 2026','65% of Dubai is buying OFF-PLAN. Are you? 2026 is the year of choice. Off-Plan: Top choice for Investors. Ready Properties: Top choice for End-Users. #EREHomes #DubaiRealEstate #OffPlanDubai #DubaiProperty2026 #Emaar','2026-04-03','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','market_update','What Actually Qualifies a Distressed Deal?','Stop calling every good price a distressed deal. In the Dubai real estate world, the term distressed is thrown around constantly. Ready to find a real deal? Link in bio. #DubaiRealEstate #DistressedDeals #PropertyInvestment #EREHomes #DubaiInvestors','2026-04-04','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','behind_scenes','Monday Meeting Reel','Success isn''t a solo mission. At ERE Homes, we believe in the power of a shared vision. Our team meetings are about mentorship, growth, and ensuring every agent has the support they need to dominate the Dubai market. We don''t just hire; we build leaders. #EREHomes #DubaiRealEstate #TeamMeeting','2026-04-06','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','market_update','Dubai Is Built on Fundamentals','Is Dubai a bubble? In 2026, Dubai isn''t built on hype but on fundamentals. Record Tourism: 17M+ visitors annually. High Yields: 6-9% rental returns globally. Don''t wait to buy a property. Buy the property and wait. #EREHomes #InvestInDubai #DubaiEconomy2026','2026-04-07','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','agent_recruitment','Agents Intro Reel — Keeley','The ERE Homes Team is growing! Meet Keeley D., our Sales Manager at ERE Homes. Driving Growth. Empowering People. Luxury Expert. DM us. #DubaiRealEstateAgent #SalesManager #EREHomes #PropertySpecialists','2026-04-08','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','new_launch','Khurrum Abra Development Reel','Private pools in every studio? Yes, really. At the Southlofts model for just AED 419k: Infinity Pool & Spa, Outdoor Cinema & BBQ Area, Mini Golf & Dog Park, 5-Year Post-Handover Payment Plan. Call us before they fly! #Southlofts #DubaiRealEstate #EREHomes','2026-04-09','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','agent_recruitment','Agents Intro Reel — Ibrahim','The ERE Homes Team is growing! Meet Ibrahim, our latest Palm Jumeirah area specialist. DM us. #DubaiRealEstateAgent #JoinTheTeam #EREHomes #PalmJumeirah #PropertySpecialists','2026-04-10','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','client_story','Keeley — 2 Deals in 48 Hours','48 Hours. 2 Deals. 1 Powerhouse. Huge shoutout to Keeley for an incredible 48 hours! Closing two deals back-to-back through relentless dedication and deep area expertise. #DubaiRealEstate #ClosedDeal #EREHomes #PropertySuccess','2026-04-11','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','behind_scenes','Team Monday Meeting — 6 Apr Clip','At ERE Homes, we don''t guess, we strategize. Our weekly market recaps dive deep into the data, analyzing everything from consumer demand to risk management. Knowledge is power. Strategy is success. #EREHomes #DubaiRealEstate #TeamMeeting','2026-04-13','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','listing','Elliot — Property New to Market','Elevated Living on the Palm. New to the market and ready for lease! Stunning villa in Palm Jumeirah. Private Pool & Outdoor Terrace. DM or contact Elliot at +971 58 531 0989. #PalmJumeirah #DubaiLuxuryRentals #NewToMarket #EREHomes','2026-04-14','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','property_tour','Khurrum Palm Video','POV: You just found the best deal on the Palm. Ultra-Luxury. Full Sea View. Starting from AED 7.5M. Ready to move in. Contact @khuramaziz5 now before they''re gone! #PalmJumeirah #DubaiLuxury #EREHomes #SeaViewApartment','2026-04-15','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','listing','Edna — Property Coming to Market','Wake up to the Burj Al Arab every single day. 3-bed apartment in Al Nabat, Shoreline — vacant and ready to move in. Direct Private Beach Access. Stunning Burj Al Arab & Sea Views. DM for price and booking. #PalmJumeirah #ShorelineApartments #EREHomes','2026-04-16','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
  ('fe5b9d70-0ad7-4447-b88a-750b927b3488','instagram','agent_recruitment','Agents Intro Reel — Nikhil','The ERE Homes Team is growing! Meet Nikhil, our latest Dubai Creek Harbour area specialist. DM us. #DubaiRealEstateAgent #JoinTheTeam #EREHomes #DubaiCreekHarbour #PropertySpecialists','2026-04-17','published',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
